            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>
        
<p>Call of Duty has made a big change with Black Ops 7 by introducing a four-player co-op campaign, which, for the first time, has exclusive Camos to unlock.</p>



<p>While earning Camos has long been part of the Call of Duty grind, with <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/black-ops-7-zombie-camo-challenges/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">exclusive Camos available in both Zombies</a> and <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/black-ops-7-multiplayer-camo-challenges/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Multiplayer</a>, Black Ops 7 adds even more to the mix with the campaign.</p>



<p>If you’re on the hunt to unlock every Camo you possibly can in Black Ops 7, keep this guide handy as it details all of the challenges to tick off.</p>







<h2 id="h-all-black-ops-7-campaign-camos-amp-challenges">All Black Ops 7 Campaign Camos &amp; Challenges</h2>



<figure><figcaption>To-do list. Image via Activision</figcaption></figure>



<p><strong>There are 12 Camos to unlock for each weapon in Black Ops 7’s co-op campaign, with nine Military Camos and three Special Camos to earn, with Mastery Camos in addition to those.</strong></p>



<p>Military Camos have the same requirements across the board, with some exceptions, while Special Camos have specific challenges to unlock.</p>



<p>Finally, there are also Mastery Camos to earn, which require unlocking all the Camos available on specific guns.</p>



<h3 id="h-all-military-camo-challenges">All Military Camo Challenges</h3>



<p><strong>There are nine Military Camos to earn in Black Ops 7 Co-Op campaign, with the requirements being the same across all weapons and requiring Critical Kills.</strong></p>



<p>The exceptions, however, are Shotguns, which require Point-Blank Kills, Melees, which just require Kills, and Launchers, which require Kills, destruction of Guild Equipment, or VTOL Destructions.</p>



